OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather grey start with some
OL,6,Fshowery outbreaks of rain. The cloud
OL,7,Fwill break up allowing some spells of
OL,8,Fsunshine, but this may also trigger
OL,9,Fsome heavier showers by the afternoon.
OL,10,FFeeling warmer, especially in any
OL,11,Fsunshine.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShowers fading this evening,
OL,14,Fleaving a dry and clear night to
OL,15,Fdevelop across the country. Turning
OL,16,Fchilly under the clear skies,
OL,17,Fespecially in the countryside.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
