OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA dry and sunny start, but
OL,6,Fcloud will tend to increase throughout
OL,7,Fthe day, with a scattering of showers
OL,8,Fdeveloping. Showers potentially
OL,9,Fturning heavier into the afternoon.
OL,10,FFeeling warm.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FEarly
OL,13,Frain clearing Sunday leaving a dry but
OL,14,Fcooler day. Remaining cooler early
OL,15,Fnext with further showers or longer
OL,16,Fspells of rain, but also some drier
OL,17,Fand sunnier interludes.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
